	<key>PayloadDescription</key>
	<string>A GUI Installer for Vynal 6
Vynal is a safe replacement for Cydia with themes,tweaks and other apps, previously only avalible to jailbroken devices. 
http://gb4iphone.x10.mx
changelog:
Updated defult package repo
Improved Installer
</string>
